data.description: Start living your dreams now instead of waiting years to create the infrastructure. It's all done for you. This carefully maintained estate offers ready-to-go options. First, an incredibly flexible barn space with separate areas and elevated ceilings that accommodate so many interests. Electric and water; RV plug in. Further, you have fenced pastures, concrete drive, natural areas (pick berries this summer from a mowed path), a lovely and private pond. Inside feels as spacious as the outside. Expansive living spaces and bedrooms, primary suite with bath and large walk in closet. Incredibly well maintained. See docs for big ticket updates incl. new windows and HVAC!  FANTASTIC opportunity for hobbyist or to work from home. Really a special property. Must see.
